Henry W. TOLL, as Trustee, v. David B. SAUVE, as Trustee, et al. No. 228. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. March 18, 1930. Stanley, H. Johnson and C. Russell Shetterly, both of Denver, Colo., for appellant.

Before LEWIS., PHILLIPS', and MeDERMOTT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed March 18, 1930, on stipulation.
